sentences: Adrienne Eliza Houghton (née Bailon; born October 24, 1983) is an American television host, singer, and actress.
Since 2013, Bailon has been a co-host of the daytime talk show The Real; for which she has since won a Daytime Emmy Award.
In 2013, Bailon became the first Latina host of a daytime talk show in the US.
She also competed in The Masked Singer in 2019 as the Flamingo, finishing in third place.
